Color in preservative.— Dorsum of head, body, and limbs uniform lavender (
Fig. 3
); upper lip cream; iris white with dark lavender reticulations; nuptial pad on Finger II cream; dorsally, Fingers II and III and Toes I– III unpigmented; venter cream.
